tuv.prop: you should lower your shoulders and lift your head higher towards the ceiling.
I'm such a big fan of yours.
you two were sleeping together, looking all beautiful and cozy!
tuv.seg: I was worried about why this wasn’t working after trying so many different things, but I'm so glad it all worked out.
me preocupaba que no pudieran dormir después de probar tantas cosas, pero me alegra que lo hayan logrado.

tuv.prop: you’re speaking nonsense, you really must be sick.
tuv.seg: I tried so hard to get into this company... if I'm gonna die, I should die here...
me esforcé tanto por entrar a esta compañía que, si muero, debería ser aquí.

tuv.prop: why didn't you do that from the beginning?!
tuv.seg: I helped you recover your strength using my demonic energy.
te ayudé a recuperarte con mi energía demoníaca.

tuv.prop: only the bodily conditions related to sleep get synchronized.
tuv.seg: it looks like you'll be dragged into everything that woman does now.
parece que, de ahora en más, esa mujer lo arrastrará a todo lo que haga.

tuv.prop: I tend not to dwell on tough or complicated problems for too long.
tuv.seg: I thought you were gonna say no.
creí que me iba a decir que no.

tuv.prop: can you put those people to sleep only when they're not in any potential danger?
tuv.seg: I told you. it's not something I choose.
ya te dije. no es mi elección.

tuv.prop: he doesn’t know much of anything.
tuv.seg: at this rate, I think I’ll have another nightmare if I fall asleep.
{i>a este ritmo, creo que tendré otra pesadilla si me vuelvo a dormir.<i}

tuv.prop: you’ll quickly forget once you go back to sleep. after all, humans are forgetful creatures.
why does she look so surprised? did I say something wrong?
tuv.seg: that’s the exact same thing he said in my dream!
{i>¡es justo lo que me dijo en mi pesadilla!<i}

tuv.prop: I guess there is one thing.
tuv.seg: it's something we need to do alone though.
pero es algo que tenemos que hacer a solas.

tuv.prop: maybe this was too much for you this late at night.
tuv.seg: it seems like confusing and disconcerting things like this happen every time I’m with her.
{i>parece que, cada vez que estoy con ella, me pasan cosas confusas y desconcertantes.<i}

tuv.prop: since I can hold you back if I get sick.
tuv.seg: you were probably worried about yourself, not me.
creo que estaba preocupado por usted, no por mí,
why is she bringing that up all of the sudden?
{i>¿por qué, de pronto, me habla de eso?<i}
anyway, what is this on my wrist...?
{i>¿qué será esto que tengo en la muñeca?<i}

tuv.prop: I knew it. he always ends up listening to me.
tuv.seg: you are going to feel each other's breathing, and maintain a similar biological rhythm.
van a sentir la respiración del otro y mantener un ritmo biológico similar.

tuv.prop: I can't use that power on humans because it's so strong that it can remove anything.
do you still not trust me, miss seohwa? when I even altered the memories of my staff to make your life easier at work?
tuv.seg: I can tell something’s bothering you... so you aren’t going to tell me about it this time either?
es evidente que algo te molesta. ¿tampoco piensas contarme esta vez?

tuv.prop: there’s something very awkward about her.
wait, he turned to face me? why?!

tuv.seg: cuando estoy contigo, me vuelvo impulsivo.
how is she seeing something I can't even see...?
¿cómo puede ser que ella vea algo que yo no?

tuv.prop: he’s been waiting for five hours
tuv.seg: I can’t see what’s happening inside very well...
no puedo ver bien lo que pasa ahí adentro.

tuv.prop: I'm also on the product development team.
I'll find a way no matter what.
do you really expect me to believe that?
tuv.seg: I know you’re making it all up.

tuv.prop: it looks like I should work on my manners.
'cause I need to go to the sauna.
tuv.seg: why are you going to the 15th floor anyway? are you going there to meet with someone?
¿y por qué vas al 15.º piso? ¿vas a reunirte con alguien ahí?

tuv.prop: I'm such a big fan of yours.
tuv.seg: I’ve worked out very hard at home to your videos!
¡gracias a sus videos, he entrenado mucho en casa!

tuv.prop: you look pale and you’re sweating profusely. what’s wrong?
tuv.seg: I was just worried because you suddenly disappeared.
me tenía preocupada porque desapareció de pronto.

tuv.prop: this is all because you keep wasting your energy working late into the night.
you make it impossible for me to mind my own business because you don't seem to do anything right.
tuv.seg: how many more times do I have to tell you to eat better and stay healthy?
¿cuántas veces tengo que repetirte que comas mejor y cuides tu salud?

tuv.prop: still, he's an expert... he must be different.
tuv.seg: what would that young trainer know about yoga? you'll learn much more from me.
¿qué puede saber sobre yoga ese entrenador mocoso? yo te enseñaré más.

tuv.prop: do you really think he abdicated the throne for no reason?
oops, that’s not what I meant to say...
tuv.seg: excuse me, miss lee? what did you just say to me?

tuv.prop: but why doesn’t he want you to return to the demon world?
so he stopped the hourglass so that you would have to stay in the human world.
tuv.seg: it's because he would do anything to become the king of the demon world.
porque haría cualquier cosa con tal de convertirse en el rey de los demonios.

tuv.prop: if someone files a complaint saying the contest wasn’t judged fairly, mr. gam will also be put in an awkward position...
tuv.seg: this is something I really wanted... but I don’t know what to do anymore.
{i>esto es lo que tanto quería, pero ya no sé qué hacer.<i}

tuv.prop: since I can't predict what will happen to me...
I have my own office though.
tuv.seg: ...you should work at this desk for now.
… debes trabajar en este escritorio por ahora.

tuv.prop: wouldn’t there be someone who knows the reason behind that?
tuv.seg: it doesn’t make sense that I’d only have forgotten everything about you.
no tiene sentido que solamente haya olvidado todo lo relacionado a ti.

tuv.prop: Chapter 27 Written by MJ Art by Baeklee
thank you so much, young lady. you saved my life.
miss seohwa, if you’re free today, let me treat you to dinner!
come to think of it, I never really liked this human. he’s always got that vacant smile on his face, like an untrained puppy.
tuv.seg: miss seohwa needs to focus on the new project launch for the time being, and so will be working late every day.
por ahora, la señorita seohwa debe enfocarse en el proyecto nuevo, por lo que trabajará hasta tarde todos los días.

tuv.prop: don’t even think about coming near this woman.
if you do, I will destroy you.
humans can get hurt very easily.
tuv.seg: it's not like anything really bad could've happened... you didn't have to...
tampoco fue para tanto. no era necesario que me…

tuv.prop: damn, look how scary you are.
tuv.seg: anyway, why are you even trying to come back? the demon world is now mine.
en fin, ¿por qué intentas regresar? ahora el mundo de los demonios me pertenece.

tuv.prop: no, we're in different rooms divided by the door.
tuv.seg: still, this is inappropriate! we're basically in the same room.
¡pero es inapropiado! es como estar en el mismo cuarto.

tuv.prop: it’ll rock gently and make you feel way more relaxed.
tuv.seg: you should try it too, mr. gam!

tuv.prop: ...drinking an americano, the cheapest menu item...
I also used to edit my job applications for hours...
so if your plan was to try and get something from me, you’d better give up.
tuv.seg: mr. gam always keeps his word. that’s why I trust him.
el señor gam es un hombre de palabra. por eso confío en él.

tuv.prop: it’s almost time to leave this place.
was the most satisfying deed I’ve accomplished in the past 600 years.
tuv.seg: providing a good night’s rest to humans...
but I want to. please just stay still.

tuv.prop: you must be tired from walking around because of me. you should rest!
tuv.seg: I wonder what those eyes were trying to say.

tuv.prop: unexpected things seem to be happening since I started living with a man.
tuv.seg: wait, he's not a man. mr. gam isn't even a human...
{i>momento, no es un hombre. el señor gam no es humano.<i}

tuv.prop: storage unit of a construction site
what? we're not even halfway through...
I’m not? but I feel great.

tuv.seg: mi “compañera” no se siente muy bien.
she didn’t even bother to give me a call!
I had no idea it would be this hard.
no imaginé que sería tan difícil.
but is it safe for him to fall asleep right in front of an open flame like that?
pero ¿será seguro que se duerma delante de la fogata?
